HEADWORD: Dollardee
<hw>Dol`lar*dee"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A species of sunfish (<spn>Lepomis pallidus</spn>), common in the
United States; -- called also <altname>blue sunfish</altname>, and
<altname>copper-nosed bream</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>dollarfish</ent>⟦br⟧
